        "created_at": "2016-11-15T01:04:04.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Jonathan, as Don says, there are no bargains at the Bistro, but it is an excellent, deep wine list (it used to be on-line, but they\u2019ve taken it down). I was there in June. They did have a couple of bottles of 375 mls late '90s de Montille 1ers \u2026 The Bresse chicken I had was great (you need 2 persons for one), definitely the highlight of a very good menu \u2026</p>",
