        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Howard Davis\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n Howard Davis:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The Bresse chicken I had was great (you need 2 persons for one), definitely the highlight of a very good menu \u2026</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Can confirm. And whilst not cheap (the bird or the booze) it does pair nicely with Coche-Dury Meursault and multiple vintages should be available on their list.</p>",
