        "created_at": "2016-11-15T19:00:06.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Jonathan H\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n Jonathan H:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Sounds like there will be a lot of good options! Can\u2019t wait to try the Bresse chicken. Thanks for the tips!</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Definitely get the Bresse, it\u2019s what they\u2019re known for. I\u2019ve found they often have decent pricing on things that have gone through the roof here. I seem to recall having good luck with Mugneret-Gibourg wines there for reasonable money, and especially the Nuit Chaignots bottling if I remember correctly.</p>",
